{"title":"Readers’ Rides: Mark’s Vintage Centurion Lemans 650B Conversion","link":"https://theradavist.com/650b-conversion/","date":1691154018000,"content":"<p><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2560\" height=\"1920\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/08/IMG_20230731_201733-scaled.jpg?fit=1024,9999&amp;quality=75\" alt srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/08/IMG_20230731_201733-scaled.jpg?w=2560&amp;quality=75 2560w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/08/IMG_20230731_201733-scaled.jpg?resize=1024,768&amp;quality=75 1024w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/08/IMG_20230731_201733-scaled.jpg?resize=2000,1500&amp;quality=75 2000w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/08/IMG_20230731_201733-scaled.jpg?resize=768,576&amp;quality=75 768w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/08/IMG_20230731_201733-scaled.jpg?resize=1800,1350&amp;quality=75 1800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/08/IMG_20230731_201733-scaled.jpg?resize=1335,1001&amp;quality=75 1335w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/08/IMG_20230731_201733-scaled.jpg?resize=700,525&amp;quality=75 700w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/08/IMG_20230731_201733-scaled.jpg?resize=1536,1152&amp;quality=75 1536w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/08/IMG_20230731_201733-scaled.jpg?resize=2048,1536&amp;quality=75 2048w\" /></p>\n<p><em>650b Conversions are a great way to swap out those skinny race tires on bigger 700c wheels for some extra supple cushioning. They are very popular in the randonneuring crowd and today, we’re featuring <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/mark.l.eastman/\" target=\"_blank\">Mark</a>‘s exceptional example, so let’s get to it!</em><span></span></p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2560\" height=\"1920\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/08/IMG_20230731_201755-scaled.jpg?fit=1024,9999&amp;quality=75\" alt srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/08/IMG_20230731_201755-scaled.jpg?w=2560&amp;quality=75 2560w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/08/IMG_20230731_201755-scaled.jpg?resize=1024,768&amp;quality=75 1024w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/08/IMG_20230731_201755-scaled.jpg?resize=2000,1500&amp;quality=75 2000w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/08/IMG_20230731_201755-scaled.jpg?resize=768,576&amp;quality=75 768w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/08/IMG_20230731_201755-scaled.jpg?resize=1800,1350&amp;quality=75 1800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/08/IMG_20230731_201755-scaled.jpg?resize=1335,1001&amp;quality=75 1335w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/08/IMG_20230731_201755-scaled.jpg?resize=700,525&amp;quality=75 700w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/08/IMG_20230731_201755-scaled.jpg?resize=1536,1152&amp;quality=75 1536w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/08/IMG_20230731_201755-scaled.jpg?resize=2048,1536&amp;quality=75 2048w\" /><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1920\" height=\"2560\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/08/IMG_20230731_201803-scaled.jpg?fit=1024,9999&amp;quality=75\" alt srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/08/IMG_20230731_201803-scaled.jpg?w=1920&amp;quality=75 1920w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/08/IMG_20230731_201803-scaled.jpg?resize=1024,1365&amp;quality=75 1024w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/08/IMG_20230731_201803-scaled.jpg?resize=2000,2667&amp;quality=75 2000w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/08/IMG_20230731_201803-scaled.jpg?resize=768,1024&amp;quality=75 768w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/08/IMG_20230731_201803-scaled.jpg?resize=1800,2400&amp;quality=75 1800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/08/IMG_20230731_201803-scaled.jpg?resize=1335,1780&amp;quality=75 1335w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/08/IMG_20230731_201803-scaled.jpg?resize=700,933&amp;quality=75 700w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/08/IMG_20230731_201803-scaled.jpg?resize=1152,1536&amp;quality=75 1152w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/08/IMG_20230731_201803-scaled.jpg?resize=1536,2048&amp;quality=75 1536w\" /></p>\n<p>This bike is a 650B conversion of a vintage Centurion Lemans bike I originally bought used for $75. All of the stock components were not great. The frame is made with Champion #5 so you know it’s got to be durable (Champion’s thickest tubing). I had built up a 650B conversion before with a vintage Univega with 650Bx38s so I knew it might work with wider tires.</p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1920\" height=\"2560\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/08/IMG_20230731_201935-scaled.jpg?fit=1024,9999&amp;quality=75\" alt srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/08/IMG_20230731_201935-scaled.jpg?w=1920&amp;quality=75 1920w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/08/IMG_20230731_201935-scaled.jpg?resize=1024,1365&amp;quality=75 1024w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/08/IMG_20230731_201935-scaled.jpg?resize=2000,2667&amp;quality=75 2000w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/08/IMG_20230731_201935-scaled.jpg?resize=768,1024&amp;quality=75 768w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/08/IMG_20230731_201935-scaled.jpg?resize=1800,2400&amp;quality=75 1800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/08/IMG_20230731_201935-scaled.jpg?resize=1335,1780&amp;quality=75 1335w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/08/IMG_20230731_201935-scaled.jpg?resize=700,933&amp;quality=75 700w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/08/IMG_20230731_201935-scaled.jpg?resize=1152,1536&amp;quality=75 1152w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/08/IMG_20230731_201935-scaled.jpg?resize=1536,2048&amp;quality=75 1536w\" /><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2560\" height=\"1920\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/08/IMG_20230731_201944-scaled.jpg?fit=1024,9999&amp;quality=75\" alt srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/08/IMG_20230731_201944-scaled.jpg?w=2560&amp;quality=75 2560w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/08/IMG_20230731_201944-scaled.jpg?resize=1024,768&amp;quality=75 1024w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/08/IMG_20230731_201944-scaled.jpg?resize=2000,1500&amp;quality=75 2000w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/08/IMG_20230731_201944-scaled.jpg?resize=768,576&amp;quality=75 768w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/08/IMG_20230731_201944-scaled.jpg?resize=1800,1350&amp;quality=75 1800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/08/IMG_20230731_201944-scaled.jpg?resize=1335,1001&amp;quality=75 1335w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/08/IMG_20230731_201944-scaled.jpg?resize=700,525&amp;quality=75 700w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/08/IMG_20230731_201944-scaled.jpg?resize=1536,1152&amp;quality=75 1536w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/08/IMG_20230731_201944-scaled.jpg?resize=2048,1536&amp;quality=75 2048w\" /></p>\n<p>Then I stumbled across a Bridgestone 650B fork. I cut and filed down the cantilever studs on the fork and repainted the frame and fork in burgundy. I also recovered a vintage Avocet Racing 1 saddle in matching burgundy and retaped the handlebars in Newbaums’ cotton tape with shellac.</p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2560\" height=\"1920\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/08/IMG_20230731_201831-scaled.jpg?fit=1024,9999&amp;quality=75\" alt srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/08/IMG_20230731_201831-scaled.jpg?w=2560&amp;quality=75 2560w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/08/IMG_20230731_201831-scaled.jpg?resize=1024,768&amp;quality=75 1024w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/08/IMG_20230731_201831-scaled.jpg?resize=2000,1500&amp;quality=75 2000w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/08/IMG_20230731_201831-scaled.jpg?resize=768,576&amp;quality=75 768w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/08/IMG_20230731_201831-scaled.jpg?resize=1800,1350&amp;quality=75 1800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/08/IMG_20230731_201831-scaled.jpg?resize=1335,1001&amp;quality=75 1335w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/08/IMG_20230731_201831-scaled.jpg?resize=700,525&amp;quality=75 700w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/08/IMG_20230731_201831-scaled.jpg?resize=1536,1152&amp;quality=75 1536w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/08/IMG_20230731_201831-scaled.jpg?resize=2048,1536&amp;quality=75 2048w\" /><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2560\" height=\"1920\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/08/IMG_20230731_201908-scaled.jpg?fit=1024,9999&amp;quality=75\" alt srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/08/IMG_20230731_201908-scaled.jpg?w=2560&amp;quality=75 2560w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/08/IMG_20230731_201908-scaled.jpg?resize=1024,768&amp;quality=75 1024w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/08/IMG_20230731_201908-scaled.jpg?resize=2000,1500&amp;quality=75 2000w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/08/IMG_20230731_201908-scaled.jpg?resize=768,576&amp;quality=75 768w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/08/IMG_20230731_201908-scaled.jpg?resize=1800,1350&amp;quality=75 1800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/08/IMG_20230731_201908-scaled.jpg?resize=1335,1001&amp;quality=75 1335w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/08/IMG_20230731_201908-scaled.jpg?resize=700,525&amp;quality=75 700w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/08/IMG_20230731_201908-scaled.jpg?resize=1536,1152&amp;quality=75 1536w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/08/IMG_20230731_201908-scaled.jpg?resize=2048,1536&amp;quality=75 2048w\" /><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2560\" height=\"1920\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/08/IMG_20230731_201914-scaled.jpg?fit=1024,9999&amp;quality=75\" alt srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/08/IMG_20230731_201914-scaled.jpg?w=2560&amp;quality=75 2560w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/08/IMG_20230731_201914-scaled.jpg?resize=1024,768&amp;quality=75 1024w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/08/IMG_20230731_201914-scaled.jpg?resize=2000,1500&amp;quality=75 2000w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/08/IMG_20230731_201914-scaled.jpg?resize=768,576&amp;quality=75 768w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/08/IMG_20230731_201914-scaled.jpg?resize=1800,1350&amp;quality=75 1800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/08/IMG_20230731_201914-scaled.jpg?resize=1335,1001&amp;quality=75 1335w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/08/IMG_20230731_201914-scaled.jpg?resize=700,525&amp;quality=75 700w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/08/IMG_20230731_201914-scaled.jpg?resize=1536,1152&amp;quality=75 1536w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/08/IMG_20230731_201914-scaled.jpg?resize=2048,1536&amp;quality=75 2048w\" /></p>\n<p>I’ve ridden a few 200k brevet rides with the San Francisco Randonneurs club previously on a SOMA Grand Randonneur with Grand Bois 650Bx42 tires and I really like these tires. While not super fast, they take rough terrain well and avoid flats.</p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2560\" height=\"1920\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/08/IMG_20230731_201857-scaled.jpg?fit=1024,9999&amp;quality=75\" alt srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/08/IMG_20230731_201857-scaled.jpg?w=2560&amp;quality=75 2560w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/08/IMG_20230731_201857-scaled.jpg?resize=1024,768&amp;quality=75 1024w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/08/IMG_20230731_201857-scaled.jpg?resize=2000,1500&amp;quality=75 2000w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/08/IMG_20230731_201857-scaled.jpg?resize=768,576&amp;quality=75 768w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/08/IMG_20230731_201857-scaled.jpg?resize=1800,1350&amp;quality=75 1800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/08/IMG_20230731_201857-scaled.jpg?resize=1335,1001&amp;quality=75 1335w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/08/IMG_20230731_201857-scaled.jpg?resize=700,525&amp;quality=75 700w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/08/IMG_20230731_201857-scaled.jpg?resize=1536,1152&amp;quality=75 1536w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/08/IMG_20230731_201857-scaled.jpg?resize=2048,1536&amp;quality=75 2048w\" /><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2560\" height=\"1920\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/08/IMG_20230731_201851-scaled.jpg?fit=1024,9999&amp;quality=75\" alt srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/08/IMG_20230731_201851-scaled.jpg?w=2560&amp;quality=75 2560w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/08/IMG_20230731_201851-scaled.jpg?resize=1024,768&amp;quality=75 1024w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/08/IMG_20230731_201851-scaled.jpg?resize=2000,1500&amp;quality=75 2000w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/08/IMG_20230731_201851-scaled.jpg?resize=768,576&amp;quality=75 768w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/08/IMG_20230731_201851-scaled.jpg?resize=1800,1350&amp;quality=75 1800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/08/IMG_20230731_201851-scaled.jpg?resize=1335,1001&amp;quality=75 1335w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/08/IMG_20230731_201851-scaled.jpg?resize=700,525&amp;quality=75 700w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/08/IMG_20230731_201851-scaled.jpg?resize=1536,1152&amp;quality=75 1536w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/08/IMG_20230731_201851-scaled.jpg?resize=2048,1536&amp;quality=75 2048w\" /><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2560\" height=\"1920\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/08/IMG_20230731_201843-scaled.jpg?fit=1024,9999&amp;quality=75\" alt srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/08/IMG_20230731_201843-scaled.jpg?w=2560&amp;quality=75 2560w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/08/IMG_20230731_201843-scaled.jpg?resize=1024,768&amp;quality=75 1024w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/08/IMG_20230731_201843-scaled.jpg?resize=2000,1500&amp;quality=75 2000w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/08/IMG_20230731_201843-scaled.jpg?resize=768,576&amp;quality=75 768w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/08/IMG_20230731_201843-scaled.jpg?resize=1800,1350&amp;quality=75 1800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/08/IMG_20230731_201843-scaled.jpg?resize=1335,1001&amp;quality=75 1335w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/08/IMG_20230731_201843-scaled.jpg?resize=700,525&amp;quality=75 700w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/08/IMG_20230731_201843-scaled.jpg?resize=1536,1152&amp;quality=75 1536w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/08/IMG_20230731_201843-scaled.jpg?resize=2048,1536&amp;quality=75 2048w\" /></p>\n<p>Some local big tech companies that had fleet 3-speed bikes using 650B wheels were frequently dumped in my neighborhood in East Palo Alto. The front dynamo wheel and lighting were repurposed from a couple of these bikes and I built-up the rear wheel with a vintage 6 speed hub and a Shimano 6-speed freewheel.</p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2560\" height=\"1920\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/08/IMG_20230731_201742-scaled.jpg?fit=1024,9999&amp;quality=75\" alt srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/08/IMG_20230731_201742-scaled.jpg?w=2560&amp;quality=75 2560w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/08/IMG_20230731_201742-scaled.jpg?resize=1024,768&amp;quality=75 1024w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/08/IMG_20230731_201742-scaled.jpg?resize=2000,1500&amp;quality=75 2000w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/08/IMG_20230731_201742-scaled.jpg?resize=768,576&amp;quality=75 768w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/08/IMG_20230731_201742-scaled.jpg?resize=1800,1350&amp;quality=75 1800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/08/IMG_20230731_201742-scaled.jpg?resize=1335,1001&amp;quality=75 1335w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/08/IMG_20230731_201742-scaled.jpg?resize=700,525&amp;quality=75 700w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/08/IMG_20230731_201742-scaled.jpg?resize=1536,1152&amp;quality=75 1536w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/08/IMG_20230731_201742-scaled.jpg?resize=2048,1536&amp;quality=75 2048w\" /> <img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2560\" height=\"1920\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/08/IMG_20230731_202033-scaled.jpg?fit=1024,9999&amp;quality=75\" alt srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/08/IMG_20230731_202033-scaled.jpg?w=2560&amp;quality=75 2560w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/08/IMG_20230731_202033-scaled.jpg?resize=1024,768&amp;quality=75 1024w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/08/IMG_20230731_202033-scaled.jpg?resize=2000,1500&amp;quality=75 2000w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/08/IMG_20230731_202033-scaled.jpg?resize=768,576&amp;quality=75 768w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/08/IMG_20230731_202033-scaled.jpg?resize=1800,1350&amp;quality=75 1800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/08/IMG_20230731_202033-scaled.jpg?resize=1335,1001&amp;quality=75 1335w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/08/IMG_20230731_202033-scaled.jpg?resize=700,525&amp;quality=75 700w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/08/IMG_20230731_202033-scaled.jpg?resize=1536,1152&amp;quality=75 1536w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/08/IMG_20230731_202033-scaled.jpg?resize=2048,1536&amp;quality=75 2048w\" /></p>\n<p>The bike rides well as a daily and is very fun and nimble with the Grand Bois Hetre 42mm wide tires. I’ve been tempted to add a front or rear rack, but it’s fun as a roadster.</p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2560\" height=\"1920\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/08/IMG_20230731_201825-scaled.jpg?fit=1024,9999&amp;quality=75\" alt srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/08/IMG_20230731_201825-scaled.jpg?w=2560&amp;quality=75 2